        <Parent_String>Shirvan [300244698], East Caucasian textile styles [300244539], Caucasian textile styles [300244537], Caucasian (culture or style) [300244536], Central Asian [300018281], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
